long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Take full control of your browser with Page Odyssey. Page Odyssey is an intuitive tool that helps you understand how you access the internet. 

► Safe and Password Protected
► Analyses and Tracks Online Footprint
► Incognito History Tracking
► Easy to Use

 Safe and Password Protected
-Protects your data from friends and family on a shared computer
-Keeps your data local to your computer for your eyes only

Analyses and Tracks Online Footprint
-Browser Level Footprint tracking
-Activity analysis
-Analyses how your browser is being used

Incognito History Tracking
-Allows Incognito History Tracking
-Understand what your browser has been accessing
-Intuitive search and history analysis

Easy to Use
-Clean ad-free user experience 
-Intuitive design and display
